## Wishlist / Account Product Grids

**Problem:** Wishlist shows one narrow card with excessive whitespace; grid doesn't fill width.

**Fix:** (1) Use `contents` on the map wrapper Box. (2) Add `xl:grid-cols-5` for wider screens. (3) Add `min-w-0` to VStack/card containers to prevent overflow. (4) Use `!bg-[var(--theme-primary)]` on Buttons for proper theme styling.

